            "description": "Get system analytics\n\nIncludes:\n- Total users by role\n- Total buses and drivers\n- Booking statistics (total, completed, cancelled, confirmed)\n- Total revenue (INR)\n\nRequires: Valid JWT token with Admin role"
          },
          "response": []
